Package: jonesctrWeather
Title: Access Jones Center Weather Station Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jones Center IT", , , "support@jonesctr.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions to authenticate and retrieve weather station data
    from the Jones Center at Ichauway weather API. Handles Entra ID
    authentication automatically using the user's @jonesctr.org account.
